nodes.text: This T-series military strategic analysis and tactics droid served in the Confederacy of Independent Systems during the Clone Wars against the Galactic Republic. The T-series military strategic analysis and tactics droid had white sensor color and light and dark plating. It stood at 1.93 meters tall.
This tactical droid is the announcer for the Confederacy of Independent Systems in the multiplayer modes of Star Wars Battlefront II.
